lead_paragraph: AS Monaco's Kamil Glik scored a fine goal in the fifth minute of stoppage time to salvage a 1-1 home draw with Bayer Leverkusen and keep them top of Champions League Group E on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Glik Strikes Late to Salvage Draw for Monaco
headline.main: Glik Strikes Late to Salvage Draw for Monaco
